<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">

   <link href="/public/assets/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=font1|font2|etc" type="text/css">
  </head>
  <body>



<div class="jumbotron text-center">
  <h1>Account Page</h1>
  <p>Your Account Page to modify your profile and see your orders</p> 
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">

  <p> This is the page where the user will "land" after they login or register </p>

  <p> Welcome back (enter name here) </p>
  
  <p> WeBuyYourGames.com offers our users the ability to sell their old games 
    for a competitive price.  Ditch those old games and systems and get paid today </P>

    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12">
      <ul> Here are the steps : 
    <ul> 1 : Click the button below </ul>
    <ul> 2 : Enter all the items you have for sale </ul>
    <ul> 3 : After you submit the items for sale we will send you a quote for your items </ul>
    <ul> 4 : Accept the price and we will send you a shipping lable to inspect the items and then send money to you </ul>
    </ul>

    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12">
    <a href="http://localhost:3000/account/new" class="btn btn-info" role="button">Sell Games Now</a>
    </div>



    <div class="col-lg-12" id="order">
       <h3>Your Orders</h3>

<h4> Order #1 </h4>
<p> Feel free to edit or delete any items in your order by clicking the delete button </p>
 
 <%items.forEach(function(item){ %>
   <p><%= item.title %> - <%= item.condition %> - <%= item.quantity %> - <%= item.description %></p>
     <form class="" action="/account/<%=item.id%>?_method=DELETE" method="post">
          <button type="submit" name="button">Delete</button>
        </form>
 <% }) %>
 
<h3 id="offer"> WeBuyYourGames.com would like to offer you : ${$xx} for order 1001 </h3>
    </div>


  </div>
</div>


